CREATE TABLE weekly_hours_by_industry (

	period_name TEXT NOT NULL, 
	value DOUBLE PRECISION NOT NULL, 
	year TEXT NOT NULL, 
	period TEXT NOT NULL, 
	title TEXT NOT NULL, 
	seriesid TEXT NOT NULL, 
	seasonal_adjustment TEXT NOT NULL, 
	industry_code CHAR(8) NOT NULL,

	CONSTRAINT weekly_hours_by_industry_pkey PRIMARY KEY (seriesid, date)
